_sText: De_dustanesi --------------- Using parts of Dust2 by Dave Johnston and Piranesi by Fingers plus some original parts such as an all-new bombsite A, de_dustanesi is a fast and action-packed remix. Enjoy! Check out the YOUTUBE flyby video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wg9cVQEHi8g Please don't forget comments and assessments. ------ CREDITS Dust2 by Dave Johnston Piranesi by Iika "Fingers" Keranen Dustanesi (remix) by Predulus / A.o.F. / SEAL ---- JUST ADDED !!! - Radar Map Overview - Navigation Place Names Server Admins - please download this latest version Apologies for any inconvenience
